Author: John Doe
Name: Statue of Liberty
Text: The Statue of Liberty is a famous monument located in New York City, symbolizing freedom and democracy.

Author: Jane Smith
Name: Eiffel Tower
Text: The Eiffel Tower is a wrought-iron lattice tower in Paris, France, and one of the most recognizable structures in the world.

Author: Alex Johnson
Name: Great Wall of China
Text: The Great Wall of China is an ancient series of walls and fortifications, stretching across northern China.
